<p dir="auto">The <code>disablePolyfillReadyClass</code> option determines if selectors are prefixed with an indicator class.
This class is only set on your document if the polyfill loads and is needed.</p>
<p dir="auto">By default this option is <code>false</code>.
Set this to <code>true</code> to prevent the class from being added.</p>
